"{\"uid\": \"news.cgtn.com-news-2024-07-19-Five-time-Olympic-race-walker-Liu-Hong-aims-to-win-gold-again-1vm6zvNkBl6-p.html\", \"text\": \"Our Privacy Statement & Cookie Policy  By continuing to browse our site you agree to our use of cookies, revised Privacy Policy and Terms of Use. You can change your cookie settings through your browser.  Copied  China will send 405 athletes, including 42 Olympic champions, to the upcoming Paris Olympic Games. The delegation includes 37-year-old race walker Liu Hong, who is embarking on her fifth Olympic journey and will be the oldest athlete. Despite her advancing age, Liu is determined to push herself to the limit and win gold.  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466\"}"